The '''''First Citizen''''' was [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]] [[Borsk Fey'lya]]'s [[Kothlis Systems]] [[Luxuflier]]. It was used to evacuate people during the [[Battle of Coruscant (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Battle of Coruscant]], as Fey'lya refused to leave [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Its [[Captain/Legends|captain]] was [[Durm]].

